<td>
Donnelley Enterprise Solutions Incorporated (DESI) is a leading single-source provider of integrated information management solutions to professional service organizations, primarily large law firms, investment banks and accounting firms. We offer our clients the opportunity to focus on their core businesses through a comprehensive array of business services outsourcing and information technology services. We provide the foundation for success through our three divisions: <b>Donnelley Business Services, LANSystems, and Systems Management Group.</b>
